title: An Essay on the Use of the Obstetrical Forceps
summary: This handwritten thesis, written by **Richard Gardiner**, was submitted to the **Homeopathic Medical College of Pennsylvania** in **Philadelphia** on **February 1, 1850** as part of the requirements for the Doctorate in Medicine. The work is a brief historical survey of obstetrical forceps, tracing their use from the earliest period of antiquity through the days of Hippocrates and Galen.
